  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Pre-feasibility study on prospects for restructuring the Danish Investment Fund for Developing Countries into a state owned development bank</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objectives of the consultancy work is to assess the prospects and consequences of converting IFU into a development bank and to identify specific questions which must be addressed and, if possible, suggestions and recommendations with regards to the strategic approach, as well as legal, institutional, financial and managerial issues.
The establishment of a development bank would be a central part of supporting Denmark&#x2019;s Strategy for Development Cooperation and enable a significant increase in Denmark&apos;s investments in the SDGs and the Paris Agreement on Climate Change. 
The development bank should accelerate and expand Denmark&#x2019;s efforts to mobilize additional private capital for investments in sustainable development.</narrative>
  </description>
